{"tid":2286735,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《夜更》奪大獎  導演「面對糟糕嘅香港」","createTime":"2020-11-15T08:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T08:52:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d420efc1616fdc891d04e01799d0bc25ce4fcba3","tid":2286735,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201115/ZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201115%2FZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BK7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=010e254c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201115%2FZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ%2F&h=413c1210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201115/ZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n《夜更》奪大獎 <br />\n導演「面對糟糕嘅香港」<br />\n<br />\n電影《十年》中執導《浮瓜》一章的導演郭臻，近日再次執導短片《夜更》先後入圍今屆金馬獎最佳劇情短片及2020年南方影展最佳劇情短片，《夜更》前日率先在南方影展打響勝鼓，拿下大獎。郭臻戴上黃色口罩，以視像接受南方影展得獎訪問，先以普通話多謝評審支持，其後特別以廣東話發言：「呢部片屬於舊年遇過嘅每一個香港人。係佢哋話我知，做香港人係可以有啲嘢proud of（值得驕傲）。」<br />\n<br />\n郭臻又指希望《夜更》可以幫助香港人釋放情緒，但又提醒：「回憶起舊年嘅自己係點樣，唔好忘記我哋憤怒，唔好忘記我哋付出好多，犧牲好多嘅手足們。無論時勢好壞，希望我哋可以攞出勇氣去面對呢個更加糟糕嘅香港。keep fighting. 」然後分別做出用手遮掩右眼及五一手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yo9pat1DyAd5JCbemplMf99q5YY=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RSLMWT75QZG5ZKKXPRNDAY55HM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyo9pat1DyAd5JCbemplMf99q5YY%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRSLMWT75QZG5ZKKXPRNDAY55HM.jpg&h=9a458f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■郭臻（圖）前晚以視像談得獎感受，希望《夜更》能助港人釋放情緒。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7Juw5wC9aquSUr0pFLen_Q2tFzk=/640x420/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNO53VB4E5BZ5JS2GZDRZ65OZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7Juw5wC9aquSUr0pFLen_Q2tFzk%3D%2F640x420%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNO53VB4E5BZ5JS2GZDRZ65OZI.jpg&h=55fa8c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照"},{"pid":"f9ec05ab85b86f2b68b31d2df55eaee9f7bc46ad","tid":2286735,"uid":105034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7a8614fdfb62964799e1ffb9b537aae1d2425d1","tid":2286735,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:52:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}